marginalia.translation:
For jokes and jests, see book 2 of 'De Oratore'; Quintilian's 'De Risu', chapter 4, book 6;
Master Secretary Wilson's 'Rhetoric', Of Delighting the Hearers and Provoking them to Laughter;
[etc] Giovanni Pontano's six books on urbane and humorous speech, especially the third; 
Adriaan van Baerland's three books on ancient and modern jokes.
